These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, pilot, entrepreneur, mechanic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, rose, daisy
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, white, red, apricot
 1. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the mechanic##1
 3. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person who growszinnia##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
 6. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
 9. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person who likes turquise and the security-guard##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5
13. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job   | mechanic    | pilot | entrepreneur    | security-guard   |
| Flower   | orchid | rose | zinnia | daisy |
| Pet           | dog       | horse   | rabbit  | cat     |
| Color     | turquise      | red   | apricot    | white    |

