 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
 4. the person playing bridge is the australian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 7. the victorian house is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the australian##7
 8. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
 9. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
10. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
11. the chinese is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
