 3. the person eating cucumber is the polish##1
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
 6. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 7. the person eating corn is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person eating kale##6
 9. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
12. the russian is the tiparillo-smoker##1

