 6. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the bongani-smoker##7
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the cain-smoker##6
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
10. the wooden house is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
11. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Hobby         | chess      | cooking   | sudoku   | puzzles       |
| House   | victorian | wooden    | cape-cod | ranch-style       |
| Game   | whist  | billiard | bridge   | backgammon     |
| Cigar         | cain   | vegafina    | bongani   | ritmeester |

