.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, apple, garlic, lime
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, zombie, sports
City: edinburgh, rome, hamburg, boston
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the person watching zombie movies is the person eating garlic##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person eating lime and the person eating apple##2
 5. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the person eating eggplant##7
 7. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
10. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food   | lime      | garlic     | apple   | eggplant    |
| Movie-Genre     | sports | zombie   | documentary | crime |
| City     | boston        | hamburg     | edinburgh  | rome      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 